# Frontend

Read `frontend/AGENTS.md` before editing the frontend.

- Stack: React 19, Vite, Tailwind, shadcn-style primitives in `src/components/ui/`
- Use semantic tokens (`bg-background`, `text-muted-foreground`) not hex or `capy-*`
- Pages use `PageHeader`; spacing `space-y-8`
- UI primitives: follow `frontend/src/components/ui/AGENTS.md` (forwardRef, displayName, FooProps, cn())
- Domain components: `frontend/src/components/AGENTS.md` — never put DataGrid or app logic in `ui/`
